Estudiantes LP won the championship in the second final match with the following line-ups:                               

Independiente (A)       Goyén;                         
                        Clausen, Villaverde, Trossero, M.E.Killer;                     
                        Giusti, Marangoni, Burruchaga, Bochini;                        
                        Calderón, Morete.                        
                        Coach: Nito Veiga.                       
Estudiantes LP          Bertero;
                        Camino, Brown, R.J. Agüero, A.E.Herrera;
                        M.Á.Russo, J.D.Ponce, Sabella, Trobbiani;
                        Trama, Gurrieri.
                        Coach: Eduardo Luján Manera.
Referee:                Arturo André Ithurralde.
Field:                  Independiente.

14': 1-0 Giusti.        
44': 1-1 Trama.         
70': 2-1 Trossero.      

Estudiantes LP won the final with the aggregate score of 3-2.   

Champion:               Club Estudiantes de La Plata.



